<h4 id="twitter">Twitter</h4>
<p>For Twitter share button, create an anchor linking to the below url</p>
<pre><code>https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text={post_caption}&amp;url={url}
</code></pre>
<p>You can use the below svg code to get the twitter button icon <sub><svg id="twitter_social_icon" viewBox="0 0 18 18" width="30px" fill="#1dcaff"><path d="M16.5,4.3c-0.6,0.2-1.1,0.4-1.8,0.5c0.6-0.4,1.1-1,1.4-1.7c-0.6,0.4-1.3,0.6-2,0.8c-0.6-0.6-1.4-1-2.2-1 c-1.7,0-3.1,1.4-3.1,3.1c0,0.2,0,0.5,0.1,0.7C6.3,6.5,4.1,5.3,2.5,3.4C2.3,3.9,2.1,4.4,2.1,5c0,1.1,0.5,2,1.4,2.6 c-0.5,0-1-0.2-1.4-0.4c0,0,0,0,0,0c0,1.5,1.1,2.8,2.5,3.1c-0.3,0.1-0.5,0.1-0.8,0.1c-0.2,0-0.4,0-0.6-0.1c0.4,1.2,1.5,2.1,2.9,2.2 c-1.1,0.8-2.4,1.3-3.8,1.3c-0.2,0-0.5,0-0.7,0c1.4,0.9,3,1.4,4.7,1.4c5.7,0,8.8-4.7,8.8-8.9c0-0.1,0-0.3,0-0.4 C15.6,5.5,16.1,4.9,16.5,4.3"></path></svg></sub></p>
